Task
Is it true that the given number is a negative even number?
Given an arbitrary number. Determine if it is a negative even number.
Create a variable number and assign it the value of an arbitrary integer. 
Create a variable isNegativeEven and assign it a boolean expression that evaluates to true if the number is even and negative, and false otherwise.

Solution
const number = -60;
const isNegativeEven = number % 2 === 0 && number < 0;
